column4: Tesla April registrations drop in key California market
column5: SAN FRANCISCO Registrations of Tesla Inc  vehicles in California  by far the largest market of the luxury electric car maker  fell 24 percent in April from a year ago  according to data from IHS Markit.

column4: UPDATE 1-Tesla April registrations drop in key California market
column5: SAN FRANCISCO  July 6 Registrations of Tesla Inc vehicles in California  by far the largest market of the luxury electric car maker  fell 24 percent in April from a year ago  according to data from IHS Markit.
